<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813933>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Morphology of Glemparon spp., ♂♂. A. Basitarsus of foreleg in G. manuka sp. nov., lateral. B. Basitarsus of foreleg in G. warra sp. nov., lateral. C. Palpus of G. orautahi sp. nov., lateral. D. Palpus of G. tomelilla sp. nov., lateral, holotype. E. Palpus of G. tomelilla sp. nov., lateral, paratype. F. Fourth flagellomere of G. manuka sp. nov., lateral. G. Fourth flagellomere of G. orautahi sp. nov., lateral. H. Fourth flagellomere of G. tomelilla sp. nov., lateral. Scale bars = 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813933/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813935>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Glemparon sagittifer Jaschhof, 2013, ♂. A. Gonocoxites, ventroposterior. B. Gonostylus, ventral. Scale bars = 0.05 mm. The numbered arrow indicates a diagnostic character (see description)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813935/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813939>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Glemparon aotearoa sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NZAC, no. CEC1419). A. Genitalia, ventral. B. Gonostylus, ventral. C. Apex of ejaculatory apodeme and tegmen, ventral. Scale bars = 0.05 mm. Numbered arrows indicate diagnostic characters (see Diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813939/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813965>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Glemparon rotoroa sp. nov., ♂♂. A, C. Holotype (NZAC, no. CEC1415). A. Genitalia, ventral. B. Ninth tergite, dorsal, paratype (NZAC, no. CEC1416). C. Apex of ejaculatory apodeme and tegmen, ventral. Scale bars = 0.05 mm. Numbered arrows indicate diagnostic characters (see Diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813965/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813937>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Glemparon tomelilla sp. nov., ♂♂. A–C. Holotype (NHRS, no. CEC1406). A. Genitalia, ventral. B. Gonostylus, ventral. C. Apex of ejaculatory apodeme, tegmen indicated, ventral. D. Tegmen, ventral, paratype (NHRS, no. CEC1407). Scale bars = 0.05 mm. Numbered arrows indicate diagnostic characters (see Diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813937/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813943>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Glemparon cervus sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NZAC, no. CEC1414). A. Genitalia, ventral. B. Gonostylus, ventral. C. Tegmen, ventral. D. Ninth tergite, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.05 mm. Numbered arrows indicate diagnostic characters (see Diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813943/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3813963>
    dc:description "Fig. 14. Glemparon rotoiti sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (NZAC, no. CEC1425). A. Genitalia, ventral. B. Apex of ninth tergite, ventral. C. Apex of ejaculatory apodeme and tegmen, ventral. Scale bars: A, C = 0.05 mm; B = 0.025 mm. Numbered arrows indicate diagnostic characters (see Diagnosis)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3813963/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

